@node History "Historia programu"

@{b}Program history @{ub}

Version @{fg shine}0.1@{fg text}      13.12.1997     

* First public version.

Version @{fg shine}0.13@{fg text}     30.12.1997     

* BUG FIXED: Missing UnlockPubScreen ()! How could I do such a silly
mistake? It caused problems to IPrefs. WB screen was still locked, so IPrefs
couldn't close it when screen mode, overscan or other preferences had been
changed. Bug reported by Krzysztof Kurdzieko.

Version @{fg shine}1.0@{fg text}      03.03.1998

* Datatypes support added.
* Filerequester if no PALETTE parameter is given.
* Removed direct IFF DR2D support (use datatype instead).

@endnode
